
                WELCOME TO TURBO VISION SOURCE CODE GENERATOR 1.0
                -------------------------------------------------

  This README file contains important information about Turbo
  Vision Source Code Generator Version 1.0. 
  For the latest information about TVGEN 1.0, 
  read  this file in its entirety.


TABLE OF CONTENTS
-----------------
1.  About TVGEN Version 1.0 and upgrades.
2.  How to Get Help
3.  Notes and Restrictions
4.  Files on the Disks

1.  ABOUT TVGEN VERSION 1.0 AND UPGRADES
-----------------------------------------
  Turbo Vision Source Code Generator bases on objectec-oriented programming,
  that is supported by Turbo Pascal 6.0 and event-driven programming that is 
  supported by Turbo Vision.TVGEN have only been created by means of Turbo
  Vision objects.This version supports only standart Turbo Vision objects and
  cannot define new objects.
  In the next version will be supported:
    - define new objects,that will be inherited from standart Turbo Vision
      objects
    - additional library that will contain a lot of interesting objects
      you will need in your daily programming
    - creating complete applications and compiling it into .EXE files
    - help on Turbo Vision       
    
